(88, 10, 'Free Skeeball Night', '<p>Machines will be on FREE PLAY from 6:30pm till closing at the following stores:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Copley - Wednesday (March 20th)</li>\r\n<li>Lakewood - Thursday (March 21st)</li>\r\n<li>Macedonia - Wednesday (March 20th)</li>\r\n<li>Mentor - Tuesday (March 19th)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>All are welcome to play... friends, family and fellow skeeball enthusiasts. So, practice up for the March 23rd tournament!</p>', '2019-03-16', 1),
(89, 10, 'Winter Skeeball Tournament', '<p>The <strong>2019 Winter Skeeball Tournament</strong> will be held Saturday (March 23rd) at the Winking Lizard Party Center (<a href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps?q=25200+Miles+Rd,+Bedford,+Ohio+44146-1322\">25200 Miles Rd, Bedford Heights</a>). Doors open at 5:00pm and matches start at 6:00pm.</p>\r\n<p>Everyone who played in the league (plus their significant other or a     friend) is welcome to attend... even if you didn\'t qualify to   partipate  in  the tournament, though you must have played in the league   to  qualify  to win prizes. Skeeball World Tour is a 21 and older   league...  as is this tournament.</p>\r\n<p>There will be a great complimentary All-You-Can-Eat Buffet, the main    tournament, the Second Chance Bracket, a huge Raffle and a guaranteed    great time!</p>\r\n<p>We will be giving away <strong>$800.00 in Amazon Gift Cards</strong> throughout the evening. You must have played at least 1 week during  this season to qualify and <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>you must be present to win!</strong></span> Here is the schedule of the  gift card drawings:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\r\n<li>7:15pm drawing for a $100 Amazon Gift Card</li>\r\n<li>8:15pm drawing for a $200 Amazon Gift Card</li>\r\n<li>9:15pm drawing for a $500 Amazon Gift Card</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The Winners of the tournament will receive \'3\' $50 Amazon Gift Cards,    while the runners up will receive \'3\' $25 Amazon Gift Cards.</p>\r\n<p>The <strong>Second Chance Bracket</strong> is back! If your team     loses in the first round of the main tournament, you can signup to keep     playing in the Second Chance Bracket. 7:15pm is the deadline to   signup.   The winners of the second chance bracket will receive \'3\' $25   Lizard   Loot Cards.</p>', '2019-03-17', 1),
(90, 10, 'Final Tournament Rankings', '<p>The season is now over and the <a href=\"/qualifiers\"><strong>TOURNAMENT RANKINGS</strong></a> have been set as \'Final\'. Teams that told us they aren\'t coming to the   tournament are not included in the rankings.</p>\r\n<p>The March 23rd tournament is right around the corner. If you see any errors or   ommisions in the rankings, please let us know ASAP.</p>\r\n<p>The printable PDF Tournament Bracket will be posted in the next day or two.</p>', '2019-03-17', 1),
(91, 10, 'Tournament Bracket', '<p>The <a title=\"2019 Winter Tournament Bracket\" href=\"/pdf/Tournament_Bracket_Online(2019_Winter).pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tournament Bracket</strong></a> for Saturday\'s event has been finalized. See you all at the Tournament!</p>', '2019-03-21', 1);